Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Singer :- Khesari Lal Yadav & Shilpi Raj
Feat :- Namrita Malla

Mere figure pe deke dhyan,
Kyon hota hai re munde pareshaan...2
Nasha mein dubal jawani hai,
Khatta angur ka paani hai,
Mera chhikh lage aluchap,
Kamariya..2 Lollypop pop,pop,pop...2

Na na na na na re, Najro se pila dungi,
Ja ja ja ja ja ja re Aaj jila jila dungi,
Tohara se jada Nasha, na baawe daaru mein,
Jawan tu de debu maja u na ba mehraru mein,
Josh mein hosh gawa doge,
Humko note nawa doge,
Jab Dance karungi hip hop,
Kamariya..2 Lollypop pop,pop,pop...2

Laakho diwane yaha aate hain kuch na karke jaate hain,
Pite hain sab kuch khate hain aa bigad ke jaate hain,
Pahile se bigdal baani,
Humke auri bigade da,
Aaj duniya dikha ke babuniya,
Sara garmi jhare da,
Chalo kahi ab chalte hain,
Tere pyar mein dhalte hain,
Karenge khub gup sup,
Kamariya..2 Lollypop pop,pop,pop...2

- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements

- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Maathalle Minchu Thanda Nannavale Ee Maayavi 
Chandranne Jhumki Maadi Itkondidlu Haayagi 
Muddaada Kannigondu 
Putta Aa Kennogondu Nakshathra Thandu Kodalenu Maayavi 

Maayavi Minugu Neenu 
Munjaane Bisilu Neenu 

Saaladhiro Haadu Neenu
Bekeniso Sanje Neenu 
 
Edheya Dhunige 
Belaku Neene
Neenaadhe Neenaadhe 

Yaariradha Rastheyalli
Santhaiso Avale Gaali  
Saagaradha Baaninalli 
Kangoliso Avale Neeli 

Samayaa Nee Ninthodhe
Avala Angayyalle 
Nanoonu Sharanaadhe 
Avala Gunginalle 

Sothe Hodhe Sothe Hodhe 

Nee Modhala Koneyaa Aase 
Nanna Edhege Hidiso Bhaashe

Anuraagadhali Konebeedhiyali 
Nanagu Ninagu Mane Maadiruve 
Olage Baralu Thada Inneke 
Kitakeele Naa Kaadhe 

Yaaro Naa Yaro Kanasalli Yaaru Iradhaga 
Nannavala Manasalli Naanage Bekitthu Jaaga
Ee Hrudhaya Mouna Aaguvaaaga 
Maathu Hege Aadali 

Huduki Hodhe Ello Dhooori 
Nine Sikka Shaayari

Sothe Hodhe Sothe Hodhe 

Nee Modhala Koneyaa Aase 
Nanna Edhege Hidiso Bhaashe

snippet.title: मेरे सपनें को मेरे छात्रों ने पूरा किया | Raushan Anand Sir | @GYANBINDUGSACADEMY|  Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
अगर आप Josh Talks को contact करना चाहते हैं और आपका Josh Talks से कोई प्रश्न हैं या कोई request है जो आप चाहते है की Josh Talks सुने तो आप हमें नीचे दिए गए नंबर पर Whatsapp करके, directly Josh Talks से अपना question या thought share कर सकते हैं। - 9311209639

इस वीडियो में, रौशन आनंद सर अपने संघर्षों और इंजीनियरिंग की तैयारी के सफर की शुरुआत के बारे में चर्चा कर रहे हैं। वे बताते हैं कि कैसे पटना जाने के लिए उन्हें अपने रिश्तेदारों से मदद मांगनी पड़ी। वे अपने माता-पिता के सपनों को न पूरा कर पाने के दुख और अपने भविष्य को लेकर अनिश्चितता के बारे में खुलकर बात करते हैं, जहां उनके सामने दो विकल्प थे: एक सरकारी नौकरी या कोचिंग की राह।  

साल 2014 से 2016 उनके जीवन में अहम रहे, जहाँ उन्होंने कई व्यक्तिगत चुनौतियों का सामना किया। इसमें उनके दादाजी का कैंसर की बीमारी और आर्थिक समस्याएं शामिल थीं, जिनके चलते दादाजी का उचित इलाज नहीं हो पाया। 2013 से 2017 के बीच का समय उनके लिए एक बड़े आर्थिक संकट का समय था, जिसमें रौशन सर ने होम ट्यूशन लेना शुरू किया और अपने गांव के अन्य निवासियों की मदद के बदले भोजन पाकर दिन काटे। उनकी मदद से कई छात्रों ने भी सफलता हासिल की।

कोविड-19 महामारी के दौरान, छात्रों की मदद करने के उनके जुनून ने उन्हें गंगा घाट पर आउटडोर क्लासेज लेने के लिए प्रेरित किया, जिसमें प्रशासन की कई पाबंदियों का सामना करना पड़ा। रौशन आनंद सर के "ज्ञान बिंदु जीएस पटना" कोचिंग ने बिहार पुलिस के 1000+ कांस्टेबलों को बनाने में मदद की। खुद रौशन सर ने भी चार बार लिखित परीक्षा पास की लेकिन फिजिकल टेस्ट में सफल नहीं हो सके। 

रौशन सर की कहानी हर उस व्यक्ति के लिए प्रेरणादायक है जो संघर्षों के बीच भी अपने सपनों का पीछा नहीं छोड़ता। उनकी मेहनत और दृढ़ निश्चय ने उन्हें अपने जीवन में सफलता के कई अवसर दिए, और आज वह अपने ज्ञान से हजारों छात्रों को मार्गदर्शन दे रहे हैं। 

In this video, Roshan Anand Sir shares the story of his struggles and the beginning of his journey toward preparing for an engineering career. He explains how he had to seek help from relatives just to reach Patna and openly talks about the pain of feeling unable to fulfill his parents’ dreams, along with the uncertainty he faced regarding his future, where he saw two paths: preparing for a government job or teaching in coaching.

The years 2014 to 2016 were critical for him, as he faced numerous personal challenges, including his grandfather’s battle with cancer and severe financial difficulties, which hindered his grandfather’s access to proper treatment. The period from 2013 to 2017 marked a significant economic crisis for him. To support himself, Roshan Sir began offering home tuition in his village, where, in exchange for teaching, he received meals and lodging from other village residents. Many of his students went on to achieve success, a testament to his dedication.

During the COVID-19 pandemic, Roshan Anand Sir’s passion for helping students led him to conduct outdoor classes on the banks of the Ganges, where he faced various administrative restrictions. His coaching institute, "Gyan Bindu GS Patna," helped over 1,000 students secure positions as constables in the Bihar Police force. Roshan Sir himself passed the written exam four times but could not clear the physical tests.

snippet.title: Vaalu Kallatho | Full Song | Gowri Naidu | Niveditha Gowda | Sandeep Sannu | Latest Love Songs 2024
snippet.description:
Listen this Song On Your Own Audio Platforms : https://bfan.link/vaalu-kallatho
Vaalu Kallatho – Latest Love Song 2024

Get ready to experience the beauty of love with the latest romantic melody from Nivriti Vibes! "Vaalu Kallatho" is a heartfelt Telugu love song set against a lush, green village backdrop, capturing the magic of romance in its purest form.

The video for "Vaalu Kallatho" is a visual treat, with heartwarming scenes between Gowri Naidu and Niveditha Gowda, set in serene village landscapes. Their chemistry shines, making every scene feel genuine and romantic. The music, composed by Sandeep Sannu, captures the essence of love with soulful melodies that will stay with you long after the song ends.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Music composer and Sung  :-SandeepSannu
Director and concept Ashok tirumani 
Music programmer and Sfx  : Vamsi Tyson 
Kids chorus :- Bhuvija Gayatri.D
Reshmitha.M
Radha manohar. B
Pavitra. V

Mix and Master by Roshan Sebastian

snippet.title: World's Highest Road on my new Hilux! ((Delhi to Ladakh Roadtrip)) 🇮🇳
snippet.description:
⭐️ Order Melodies of India (book) : https://melodiesofindia.com/
⭐️Join our Storytelling MasterClass for Youtube : https://monkeymagic.wtf/

Subscribe to Monkey Magic ((casual)) 
https://www.youtube.com/@UCF09HPp8qsoji3fc2gPIuoQ 
===========================================================

Baljeet ko test karne ka time aagya hai, chalo chale 🥳

Devenko :  https://www.instagram.com/devenko26/
Monkey Magic : https://www.instagram.com/monkeyxmagic/
BigBroBaljeet :  https://www.instagram.com/bigbrobaljeet/

===========================================================
📧 Email 📧 : monkeymagic@create.wtf 
===========================================================

In this video we do a roadtrip starting from New Delhi driving all the way to Demchok, LAC. We spend some two nights in Hanle, mesmerised by the stargazing experience, went to Umingla - which is world's highest motorable pass! 

About My Hilux (Baljeet) 
After almost a decade of waiting I finally have this, this what you see here is my love, is the sole reason I have worked so hard over the last years. I have had this impossible dream of driving from New Delhi to London since 2012-2014 now, but when I see 2014 I see this as an important dream. Our first car in 2013 was a second hand Maruti Suzuki Alto and to be able to reach here today has been a lot of sweat, sleepless nights and prayers!

But you see, today I'm here and this is just the start of my impossible dream. To be able to go anywhere, live anywhere. To be free on the road & off road.. I shall have my freedom and this beast that you see here today is just what will give me my freedom.

Everyone, meet Baljeet, that is going to take me & you to lots and lots of far off places. Let the adventure begin!

===========================================================
📧 Email 📧 : monkeymagic@create.wtf 

Tags : Monkey Magic Hilux, Monkey Magic New Car, Monkey Magic Roadtrip hilux, Monkey Mgaic Hilux Ladakh,

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 11 Teaser - 7th November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Sporting CP 4-1 Man City | Foden, Gyorkeres hat-trick & Araujo goals
snippet.description:
City suffered a night of Champions League disappointment, losing out 4-1 at Sporting CP with Viktor Gyokeres hitting a hat-trick for the hosts.

Pep Guardiola’s side had got off to a flying start in Lisbon going ahead thanks to a fourth minute goal from Phil Foden.

The Blues – who handed teenage defender Jahmai Simpson-Pusey a full debut – dominated the first half carving out a host of other chances.

But, out of nowhere, Gyokeres struck to level affairs late in the first half before Sporting then scored twice within three minutes at the start of the second half through Maximiliano Araujo and Gyokeres, via a penalty, to seize control.

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Blesso Cosmetics

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Sharda Sinha Death: 'Bihar Kokila' Synonymous With Chhath Songs Passes Away During Festival At 72
snippet.description:
Sharda Sinha Death: 'Bihar Kokila' Synonymous With Chhath Songs Passes Away During Festival At 72

Renowned Bihari singer Sharda Sinha, known as the 'Bihar Kokila,' passes away at 72. Sinha was in critical condition on ventilator support after her hospitalization. Her health declined shortly after the death of her husband, Brajkishore Sinha, in September. Sharda's son Anshuman confirms her passing, mourning both a beloved mother and an iconic artist. Known for traditional wedding and Chhath songs in Bhojpuri, Sinha made a lasting impact on the music scene. Her music celebrated cultural festivals, making her a cherished figure in the industry.

Known for his compassionate approach, he runs the Asian Children’s Hospital, where he treats young patients with a unique combination of medical expertise and empathy. Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Blesso Cosmetics

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.description:
Jhankar Music Gujarati Presents Latest Love Video Song titled "Hu Tane Joya Karu" Sung by Rakesh Barot, Penned by Ketan Barot, & Music Composed by Rakesh Barot & Mehul Barot & Starring : Rakesh Barot, Viyona Patil, & Concept & Director Anand Mehra
Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQeljbfXMX_5a2_KMXTkF-A/join  

Our beloved superstar, Rakesh Barot, is back with a new gujarati song, "Hu Tane Joya Karu." this touching love song..  

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐞𝐞𝐥𝐬 𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤 : https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/917379669938095/

All Streaming Store Iink : https://orcd.co/hutanejoyakaru


🎧 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐨 𝐂𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐬 : 
♪ Song : Hu Tane Joya Karu 
♪ Singer : Rakesh Barot
♪ Lyrics : Ketan Barot
♪ Music : Rakesh Barot, Mehul Barot
♪ Studio : Dhoon Digital Recording Studio, Adalaj

#rakeshbarot #gujaratinewsong #gujrativdeosong #jhankarmusicgujarati 

🎬 𝐅𝐮𝐥𝐥 𝐕𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐨 𝐂𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐬 : 
♪ Producer : MAARSS MOVIES AND MUSIC (JHANKAR MUSIC)
♪ Executive Producer : Red Velvet Cinema 
♪ Project Lead By : Chandu Raval
♪ Starring  : Rakesh Barot, Viyona Patil
♪ Co Artist : Kaushik Goswami
♪ Concept & Director : Anand Mehra
♪ D.O.P : Chirag Kachhaliya
♪ Editing : Ravindra S Rathod
♪ Creative Producer: Dhyey Films & Team
♪ Production : Rahul Rathod
♪ Choreographer : Deepak Turi 
♪ Makeup-Hair : Hasmukh Limbachiya
♪ Rakesh Barot Costume : Manisha R Barot, Vishva Selection
♪ Light : Lala Bhai
♪ Spot : Akashay Vaghela, Raju
♪ Poster : Raj Charoliya
♪ Ganre : Love Song
♪ Music Label: Jhankar Music

-------------------------------- 
📝 𝐋𝐲𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬: Gujarati  👇 

હે મારી ઘર ની ગેલેરી માં ઉભો... ( ૨)
ઉભો હું તને જોયા કરું 
હે તુ તો લાગે છે એક દમ અલગ રે
દિલ થી હુ તને પ્રેમ કરું
હે આજુ બાજુ માં મારી ચોય નજર ના પડે
ઘર આગળ તુ તો આંટા ફેરા રે કરે
હે મારા ઘર ની ગેલેરી માં ઉભો 
ઉભો હું તને જોયા કરું 
હે તુ તો લાગે છે એક દમ અલગ રે
દિલ થી  હું તને પ્રેમ કરું...

હો લઈને સાયકલ તુ તો દૂધ લેવા આવે
મારા હામે જોઈ ને તુ તો મેઠું મેઠું મલકે
હો રોજ નવા કપડા પેરી તૈયર થઈ ને ફરે 
સરમાઈ જતી જો તારી મારી નજર મળે
હે જોરદાર લાગે તુ તો મને બહુ ગમે
તારા પાછળ થઇ ગયા દિવાના અમે
હે મારા હોના જેવા દિલ મેં તને રાખુ  ... ( ૨)
રાખી ને તને હાચો પ્રેમ કરું 
હે તુ તો લાગે છે એક દમ અલગ રે
દિલ થી હું તને પ્રેમ કરું... 

હો દિલ દઈ બેઠો હુ તો તને પલવાર માં
મુડ થાય મસ્ત તને જોવુ તો હવાર માં
હો તારી મારી વાતચિત જોણે કયારે થશે
મન માં એવુ થાય આવી જાવુ તારી પાહે
હે તારી જોડે રેવા નો વિચાર રે ફરે
પરણી ને લાવી દઉ હુ તો મારા ઘરે
હે મારી જીગર જાન તને હુ તો મોનુ ... ( ૨)
મોની ને તારી હારે જીવુ 
હે તુ તો લાગે છે એક દમ અલગ રે
દિલ થી હુ તને પ્રેમ કરું 
હે મારા ઘર ની ગેલેરી માં ઉભો
ઉભો હું તને જોયા કરું ... ( ૨)

📝 𝐋𝐲𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬: English  👇

He Mari Ghar Ni Geleri Ma Ubho... (2)
Ubho Hu Tane Joya Karu 
He Tu To Lage Chhe Ek Dam Alag Re
Dil Thi Hu Tane Prem Karu
He Aaju Baju Ma mari Choy Najar Na Pade
Ghar Aagal Tu To Aanta Fera Re Kare
He Mara Ghar Ni Geleri Ma Ubho 
Ubho Hu Tane Joya Karu 
He Tu To Lage Chhe Ek Dam Alag Re
Dil Thi Hu Tane Prem Karu 

Ho Laine Cycle Tu To Dudh Leva Aave
Mara Hame Joi Ne Tu To Methu Methu Malake
Ho Roj Nava Kapda Peri Taiyar Thai Ne Fare 
Sarmai Jati Jo Tari Mari Najar Male
He Jordar Lage Tu To Mane Bahu Game
Tara Pachhal Thai Gaya Deewana Ame
He Mara Hona Jeva Dil Me Tane Rakhu... (2) 
Rakhi Ne Tane Hacho Prem Karu 
He Tu To Lage Chhe Ek Dam Alag Re
Dil Thi Hu Tane Prem Karu

Ho Dil Dai Betho Hu To Tane Palvar Ma
Mud Thay Mast Tane Jovu To Havar Ma  
Ho Tari Mari Vatchit Jane Kayare Thashe
Maan Ma Aevu Thay Aavi Javu Tari Pahe 
He Tari Jode Reva No Vichar Re Fare
Parni Ne lavi Dau Hu To Mara Ghare
He Mara Jigar Jaan Tane Hu To Monu... (2)
Moni Ne Tari Hare Jivu 
He Tu To Lage Chhe Ek Dam Alag Re
Dil Thi Hu Tane Prem Karu 
He Mara Ghar Ni Geleri Ma Ubho 
Ubho Hu Tane Joya Karu... (2)
---------------------------

snippet.title: Skoda Kylaq - The Perfect Skoda for India | First Look
snippet.description: The much anticipated Skoda Kylaq - the sub-4 metre compact SUV - finally made its debut in India today. Interestingly the company also revealed the introductory price of its base trim. It’s priced at Rs 7.89 lacs (ex-showroom), thus making it the most affordable car from the brand. Based on the same MQB A0-IN platform, the Kushaq features the same 1.0L TSI (113bhp, 178Nm) that also powers the Slavia and Kushaq. Much like its siblings, this too will be made available with both 6-speed AT and 6-speed MT. To offer better ride quality, Skoda has also reworked on its suspension compared to the Kushaq. It’s 3995mm in length, and has a wheelbase of 2556mm and ground clearance of 189mm.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jethalal and Sodhi got into a fight because they wanted to return Babita's scarf first. However, Popatlala enters their mess and destroys their focus. In front of Babita and the other members of the society, Jethalal and Iyer appear to grab the scarf from one another in order to announce themselves the winners. Will Babita and the members of the society have decided who will win between Iyer and Jethalal?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1587
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Jo Jetha Wahi Sikander' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTWbYoG3SaD_hKNC0g53ugi

                                                                                                                                                                                                   TV actors Divya Sreedhar and Kris Venugopal, who recently tied the knot on October 30, 2024, they have become the latest victims of cyber trolls who abused them for their age difference. .

Both are tv actors , Divya is famous for her negative roles in Malayalam and Tamil serials,  Kris is familiar grandfather in Patharamattu. They met on the set of Patharamattu and became friends, and with some help from Kris’s relative, their friendship turned into love.                                                                                             Kris proposed to Divya, and she happily accepted. They had a small, traditional wedding ceremony at Guruvayur Temple with close family and friends.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4235 -Jethalal ka Babita Ji ko Diwali Wish! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)

snippet.description:

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
Like our work and want to JOIN us? Please fill the applicable form and we will get in touch with you!

Join as a Geopolitical, History, Political Science Writer  → https://forms.gle/hKCwEETKhfiUHY7F7
Join as a Video Editor  → https://forms.gle/GLUS7oNYs4ESxFEF9

Perks of joining us:

1. Massive social impact on millions of minds through your work.
2. Being a part of one of the Largest YouTube Media Companies with 6 thriving YT Channels into varied genres, learn the ins and outs of social media, the new age skill.
3. A safe work environment of like-minded vision-sharing people.
4. Salary compensation: Better than industry standards while doing what you love.
5. Getsetfly is known for its superb, artistic editing. Work and learn from one of the best, most creative and skilled editing teams proficient in producing high-quality documentaries.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

Today, you'll find many toothpaste brands in the market claiming that they can whiten your teeth in just 2-3 days. For example, toothpastes promising shiny white teeth in just 3 days. Then there are creative products like this Whitening Kit, which claims to whiten your teeth in 7 days with fancy blue LEDs, or these whitening pens, that promise to instantly whiten your teeth. But are all these claims true, or are they just gimmicks? On the other hand, many dentists claim that we don’t even need toothpaste; we can keep our mouths germ-free and clean with just water and a brush. So, who’s right and who’s wrong? Today, we’re going to understand the fundamental science behind teeth whitening and yellowing so that after watching this video, you’ll be able to develop habits and routines that make your teeth visibly whiter. Let’s make a goal today to improve at least 2 lakh smiles, and let’s start this video with a like!
